{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0001", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 1, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [1]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「君薨而世子生，如之何？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「君薨而世子生，如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0002", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 2, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [2]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「卿、大夫、士從攝主，北面，於西階南。大祝裨冕，執束帛，升自西階盡等，不升堂，命毋哭。祝聲三，告曰：『某之子生，敢告。』升，奠幣于殯東几上，哭，降。眾主人、卿、大夫、士，房中，皆哭不踴。盡一哀，反位。遂朝奠。小宰升舉幣。三日，眾主人、卿、大夫、士，如初位，北面。大宰、大宗、大祝皆裨冕。少師奉子以衰；祝先，子從，宰宗人從。入門，哭者止，子升自西階。殯前北面。祝立于殯東南隅。祝聲三曰：『某之子某，從執事，敢見。』子拜稽顙哭。祝、宰、宗人、眾主人、卿、大夫、士，哭踴三者三，降東反位，皆袒，子踴，房中亦踴三者三。襲衰，杖，奠出。大宰命祝史，以名遍告于五祀山川。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「卿、大夫、士從攝主，北面，於西階南。大祝裨冕，執束帛，升自西階盡等，不升堂，命毋哭。祝聲三，告曰：『某之子生，敢告。』升，奠幣于殯東几上，哭，降。眾主人、卿、大夫、士，房中，皆哭不踴。盡一哀，反位。遂朝奠。小宰升舉幣。三日，眾主人、卿、大夫、士，如初位，北面。大宰、大宗、大祝皆裨冕。少師奉子以衰；祝先，子從，宰宗人從。入門，哭者止，子升自西階。殯前北面。祝立于殯東南隅。祝聲三曰：『某之子某，從執事，敢見。』子拜稽顙哭。祝、宰、宗人、眾主人、卿、大夫、士，哭踴三者三，降東反位，皆袒，子踴，房中亦踴三者三。襲衰，杖，奠出。大宰命祝史，以名遍告于五祀山川。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0003", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 3, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [3]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「如已葬而世子生，則如之何？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「如已葬而世子生，則如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0004", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 4, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [4]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「大宰、大宗從大祝而告于禰。三月，乃名于禰，以名遍告及社稷宗廟山川。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「大宰、大宗從大祝而告于禰。三月，乃名于禰，以名遍告及社稷宗廟山川。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0005", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 5, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [5]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「諸侯適天子，必告于祖，奠于禰。冕而出視朝，命祝史告於社稷、宗廟、山川。乃命國家五官而後行，道而出。告者，五日而遍，過是，非禮也。凡告，用牲幣。反，亦如之。諸侯相見，必告于禰，朝服而出視朝。命祝史告于五廟所過山川。亦命國家五官，道而出。反，必親告于祖禰。乃命祝史告至于前所告者，而後聽朝而入。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「諸侯適天子，必告于祖，奠于禰。冕而出視朝，命祝史告於社稷、宗廟、山川。乃命國家五官而後行，道而出。告者，五日而遍，過是，非禮也。凡告，用牲幣。反，亦如之。諸侯相見，必告于禰，朝服而出視朝。命祝史告于五廟所過山川。亦命國家五官，道而出。反，必親告于祖禰。乃命祝史告至于前所告者，而後聽朝而入。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0006", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 6, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [6]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「并有喪，如之何？何先何後？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「并有喪，如之何？何先何後？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0007", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 7, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [7]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「葬，先輕而後重；其奠也，先重而後輕；禮也。自啟及葬，不奠，行葬不哀次；反葬奠，而後辭於殯，逐修葬事。其虞也，先重而後輕，禮也。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「葬，先輕而後重；其奠也，先重而後輕；禮也。自啟及葬，不奠，行葬不哀次；反葬奠，而後辭於殯，逐修葬事。其虞也，先重而後輕，禮也。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0008", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 8, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [8]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「宗子雖七十，無無主婦；非宗子，雖無主婦可也。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「宗子雖七十，無無主婦；非宗子，雖無主婦可也。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0009", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 9, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [9]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「將冠子，冠者至，揖讓而入，聞齊衰大功之喪，如之何？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「將冠子，冠者至，揖讓而入，聞齊衰大功之喪，如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0010", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 10, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [10]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「內喪則廢，外喪則冠而不醴，徹饌而掃，即位而哭。如冠者未至，則廢。如將冠子而未及期日，而有齊衰、大功、小功之喪，則因喪服而冠。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「內喪則廢，外喪則冠而不醴，徹饌而掃，即位而哭。如冠者未至，則廢。如將冠子而未及期日，而有齊衰、大功、小功之喪，則因喪服而冠。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0011", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 11, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [11]", "text_original": "「除喪不改冠乎？」", "text_normalized": "「除喪不改冠乎？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0012", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 12, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [12]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「天子賜諸侯大夫冕弁服於大廟，歸設奠，服賜服，於斯乎有冠醮，無冠醴。父沒而冠，則已冠掃地而祭於禰；已祭，而見伯父、叔父，而後饗冠者。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「天子賜諸侯大夫冕弁服於大廟，歸設奠，服賜服，於斯乎有冠醮，無冠醴。父沒而冠，則已冠掃地而祭於禰；已祭，而見伯父、叔父，而後饗冠者。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0013", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 13, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [13]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「祭如之何則不行旅酬之事矣？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「祭如之何則不行旅酬之事矣？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0014", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 14, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [14]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「聞之：小祥者，主人練祭而不旅，奠酬於賓，賓弗舉，禮也。昔者，魯昭公練而舉酬行旅，非禮也；孝公大祥，奠酬弗舉，亦非禮也。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「聞之：小祥者，主人練祭而不旅，奠酬於賓，賓弗舉，禮也。昔者，魯昭公練而舉酬行旅，非禮也；孝公大祥，奠酬弗舉，亦非禮也。」", "notes": ""}
