{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0028", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 28, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [28]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「婿使人吊。如婿之父母死，則女之家亦使人吊。父喪稱父，母喪稱母。父母不在，則稱伯父世母。婿，已葬，婿之伯父致命女氏曰：『某之子有父母之喪，不得嗣為兄弟，使某致命。』女氏許諾，而弗敢嫁，禮也。婿，免喪，女之父母使人請，婿弗取，而後嫁之，禮也。女之父母死，婿亦如之。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「婿使人吊。如婿之父母死，則女之家亦使人吊。父喪稱父，母喪稱母。父母不在，則稱伯父世母。婿，已葬，婿之伯父致命女氏曰：『某之子有父母之喪，不得嗣為兄弟，使某致命。』女氏許諾，而弗敢嫁，禮也。婿，免喪，女之父母使人請，婿弗取，而後嫁之，禮也。女之父母死，婿亦如之。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0029", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 29, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [29]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「親迎，女在涂，而婿之父母死，如之何？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「親迎，女在涂，而婿之父母死，如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0030", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 30, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [30]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「女改服布深衣，縞總以趨喪。女在途，而女之父母死，則女反。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「女改服布深衣，縞總以趨喪。女在途，而女之父母死，則女反。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0031", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 31, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [31]", "text_original": "「如婿親迎，女未至，而有齊衰大功之喪，則如之何？」", "text_normalized": "「如婿親迎，女未至，而有齊衰大功之喪，則如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0032", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 32, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [32]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「男不入，改服於外次；女入，改服於內次；然後即位而哭。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「男不入，改服於外次；女入，改服於內次；然後即位而哭。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0033", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 33, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [33]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「除喪則不復昏禮乎？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「除喪則不復昏禮乎？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0034", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 34, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [34]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「祭，過時不祭，禮也；又何反於初？」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「祭，過時不祭，禮也；又何反於初？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0035", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 35, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [35]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「嫁女之家，三夜不息燭，思相離也。取婦之家，三日不舉樂，思嗣親也。三月而廟見，稱來婦也。擇日而祭於禰，成婦之義也。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「嫁女之家，三夜不息燭，思相離也。取婦之家，三日不舉樂，思嗣親也。三月而廟見，稱來婦也。擇日而祭於禰，成婦之義也。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0036", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 36, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [36]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「女未廟見而死，則如之何？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「女未廟見而死，則如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0037", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 37, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [37]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「不遷於祖，不祔於皇姑，婿不杖、不菲、不次，歸葬于女氏之黨，示未成婦也。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「不遷於祖，不祔於皇姑，婿不杖、不菲、不次，歸葬于女氏之黨，示未成婦也。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0038", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 38, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [38]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「取女，有吉日而女死，如之何？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「取女，有吉日而女死，如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0039", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 39, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [39]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「婿齊衰而吊，既葬而除之。夫死亦如之。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「婿齊衰而吊，既葬而除之。夫死亦如之。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0040", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 40, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [40]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「喪有二孤，廟有二主，禮與？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「喪有二孤，廟有二主，禮與？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0041", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 41, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [41]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「天無二日，土無二王，嘗禘郊社，尊無二上。未知其為禮也。昔者齊桓公亟舉兵，作偽主以行。及反，藏諸祖廟。廟有二主，自桓公始也。喪之二孤，則昔者衛靈公適魯，遭季桓子之喪，衛君請吊，哀公辭不得命，公為主，客人吊。康子立於門右，北面；公揖讓升自東階，西鄉；客升自西階吊。公拜，興，哭；康子拜稽顙於位，有司弗辯也。今之二孤，自季康子之過也。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「天無二日，土無二王，嘗禘郊社，尊無二上。未知其為禮也。昔者齊桓公亟舉兵，作偽主以行。及反，藏諸祖廟。廟有二主，自桓公始也。喪之二孤，則昔者衛靈公適魯，遭季桓子之喪，衛君請吊，哀公辭不得命，公為主，客人吊。康子立於門右，北面；公揖讓升自東階，西鄉；客升自西階吊。公拜，興，哭；康子拜稽顙於位，有司弗辯也。今之二孤，自季康子之過也。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0042", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 42, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [42]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「古者師行，必以遷廟主行乎？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「古者師行，必以遷廟主行乎？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0043", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 43, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [43]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「天子巡守，以遷廟主行，載于齊車，言必有尊也。今也取七廟之主以行，則失之矣。當七廟、五廟無虛主；虛主者，唯天子崩，諸侯薨與去其國，與祫祭於祖，為無主耳。吾聞諸老聃曰：天子崩，國君薨，則祝取群廟之主而藏諸祖廟，禮也。卒哭成事而後，主各反其廟。君去其國，大宰取群廟之主以從，禮也。祫祭於祖，則祝迎四廟之主。主，出廟入廟必蹕；老聃云。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「天子巡守，以遷廟主行，載于齊車，言必有尊也。今也取七廟之主以行，則失之矣。當七廟、五廟無虛主；虛主者，唯天子崩，諸侯薨與去其國，與祫祭於祖，為無主耳。吾聞諸老聃曰：天子崩，國君薨，則祝取群廟之主而藏諸祖廟，禮也。卒哭成事而後，主各反其廟。君去其國，大宰取群廟之主以從，禮也。祫祭於祖，則祝迎四廟之主。主，出廟入廟必蹕；老聃云。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0044", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 44, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [44]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「古者師行，無遷主，則何主？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「古者師行，無遷主，則何主？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0045", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 45, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [45]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「主命。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「主命。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0046", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 46, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [46]", "text_original": "問曰：「何謂也？」", "text_normalized": "問曰：「何謂也？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0047", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 47, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [47]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「天子、諸侯將出，必以幣帛皮圭告于祖禰，遂奉以出，載于齊車以行。每舍，奠焉而後就舍。反必告，設奠卒，斂幣玉，藏諸兩階之間，乃出。蓋貴命也。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「天子、諸侯將出，必以幣帛皮圭告于祖禰，遂奉以出，載于齊車以行。每舍，奠焉而後就舍。反必告，設奠卒，斂幣玉，藏諸兩階之間，乃出。蓋貴命也。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0048", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 48, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [48]", "text_original": "子游問曰：「喪慈母如母，禮與？」", "text_normalized": "子游問曰：「喪慈母如母，禮與？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0049", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 49, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [49]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「非禮也。古者，男子外有傅，內有慈母，君命所使教子也，何服之有？昔者，魯昭公少喪其母，有慈母良，及其死也，公弗忍也，欲喪之，有司以聞，曰：『古之禮，慈母無服，今也君為之服，是逆古之禮而亂國法也；若終行之，則有司將書之以遺後世。無乃不可乎！』公曰：『古者天子練冠以燕居。』公弗忍也，遂練冠以喪慈母。喪慈母，自魯昭公始也。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「非禮也。古者，男子外有傅，內有慈母，君命所使教子也，何服之有？昔者，魯昭公少喪其母，有慈母良，及其死也，公弗忍也，欲喪之，有司以聞，曰：『古之禮，慈母無服，今也君為之服，是逆古之禮而亂國法也；若終行之，則有司將書之以遺後世。無乃不可乎！』公曰：『古者天子練冠以燕居。』公弗忍也，遂練冠以喪慈母。喪慈母，自魯昭公始也。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0050", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 50, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [50]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「諸侯旅見天子，入門，不得終禮，廢者幾？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「諸侯旅見天子，入門，不得終禮，廢者幾？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0051", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 51, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [51]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「四。」請問之。曰：「大廟火，日食，後之喪，雨沾服失容，則廢。如諸侯皆在而日食，則從天子救日，各以其方色與其兵。大廟火，則從天子救火，不以方色與兵。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「四。」請問之。曰：「大廟火，日食，後之喪，雨沾服失容，則廢。如諸侯皆在而日食，則從天子救日，各以其方色與其兵。大廟火，則從天子救火，不以方色與兵。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0052", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 52, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [52]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「諸侯相見，揖讓入門，不得終禮，廢者幾？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「諸侯相見，揖讓入門，不得終禮，廢者幾？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0053", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 53, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [53]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「六。」請問之。曰：「天子崩，大廟火，日食，後夫人之喪，雨沾服失容，則廢。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「六。」請問之。曰：「天子崩，大廟火，日食，後夫人之喪，雨沾服失容，則廢。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0054", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 54, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [54]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「天子嘗禘郊社五祀之祭，簠簋既陳，天子崩，後之喪，如之何？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「天子嘗禘郊社五祀之祭，簠簋既陳，天子崩，後之喪，如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0055", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 55, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [55]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「廢。」曾子問曰：「當祭而日食，太廟火，其祭也如之何？」孔子曰：「接祭而已矣。如牲至，未殺，則廢。天子崩，未殯，五祀之祭不行；既殯而祭，其祭也，尸入，三飯不侑，酳不酢而已矣。自啟至于反哭，五祀之祭不行；已葬而祭，祝畢獻而已。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「廢。」曾子問曰：「當祭而日食，太廟火，其祭也如之何？」孔子曰：「接祭而已矣。如牲至，未殺，則廢。天子崩，未殯，五祀之祭不行；既殯而祭，其祭也，尸入，三飯不侑，酳不酢而已矣。自啟至于反哭，五祀之祭不行；已葬而祭，祝畢獻而已。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0056", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 56, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [56]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「諸侯之祭社稷，俎豆既陳，聞天子崩、後之喪、君薨、夫人之喪，如之何？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「諸侯之祭社稷，俎豆既陳，聞天子崩、後之喪、君薨、夫人之喪，如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0057", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 57, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [57]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「廢。自薨比至於殯，自啟至于反哭，奉帥天子。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「廢。自薨比至於殯，自啟至于反哭，奉帥天子。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0058", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 58, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [58]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「大夫之祭，鼎俎既陳，籩豆既設，不得成禮，廢者幾？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「大夫之祭，鼎俎既陳，籩豆既設，不得成禮，廢者幾？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0059", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 59, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [59]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「九。」請問之。曰：「天子崩、後之喪、君薨、夫人之喪、君之大廟火、日食、三年之喪、齊衰、大功，皆廢。外喪自齊衰以下，行也。其齊衰之祭也，尸入，三飯不侑，酳不酢而已矣；大功酢而已矣；小功、緦，室中之事而已矣。士之所以異者，緦不祭，所祭於死者無服則祭。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「九。」請問之。曰：「天子崩、後之喪、君薨、夫人之喪、君之大廟火、日食、三年之喪、齊衰、大功，皆廢。外喪自齊衰以下，行也。其齊衰之祭也，尸入，三飯不侑，酳不酢而已矣；大功酢而已矣；小功、緦，室中之事而已矣。士之所以異者，緦不祭，所祭於死者無服則祭。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0060", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 60, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [60]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「三年之喪，吊乎？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「三年之喪，吊乎？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0061", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 61, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [61]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「三年之喪，練，不群立，不旅行。君子禮以飾情，三年之喪而吊哭，不亦虛乎？」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「三年之喪，練，不群立，不旅行。君子禮以飾情，三年之喪而吊哭，不亦虛乎？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0062", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 62, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [62]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「大夫、士有私喪，可以除之矣，而有君服焉，其除之也如之何？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「大夫、士有私喪，可以除之矣，而有君服焉，其除之也如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0063", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 63, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [63]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「有君喪服於身，不敢私服，又何除焉？於是乎有過時而弗除也。君之喪，服除而後殷祭，禮也。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「有君喪服於身，不敢私服，又何除焉？於是乎有過時而弗除也。君之喪，服除而後殷祭，禮也。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0064", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 64, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [64]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「父母之喪，弗除可乎？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「父母之喪，弗除可乎？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0065", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 65, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [65]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「先王制禮，過時弗舉，禮也；非弗能勿除也，患其過於制也，故君子過時不祭，禮也。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「先王制禮，過時弗舉，禮也；非弗能勿除也，患其過於制也，故君子過時不祭，禮也。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0066", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 66, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [66]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「君薨，既殯，而臣有父母之喪，則如之何？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「君薨，既殯，而臣有父母之喪，則如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0067", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 67, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [67]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「歸居于家，有殷事，則之君所，朝夕否。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「歸居于家，有殷事，則之君所，朝夕否。」", "notes": ""}
