{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0069", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 69, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [69]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「歸哭而反送君。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「歸哭而反送君。」", "notes": ""}
