{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0071", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 71, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [71]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「歸殯，反于君所，有殷事則歸，朝夕否。大夫，室老行事；士，則子孫行事。大夫內子，有殷事，亦之君所，朝夕否。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「歸殯，反于君所，有殷事則歸，朝夕否。大夫，室老行事；士，則子孫行事。大夫內子，有殷事，亦之君所，朝夕否。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0072", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 72, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [72]", "text_original": "賤不誄貴，幼不誄長，禮也。唯天子，稱天以誄之。諸侯相誄，非禮也。", "text_normalized": "賤不誄貴，幼不誄長，禮也。唯天子，稱天以誄之。諸侯相誄，非禮也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0073", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 73, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [73]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「君出疆以三年之戒，以椑從。君薨，其入如之何？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「君出疆以三年之戒，以椑從。君薨，其入如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0074", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 74, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [74]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「共殯服，則子麻，弁絰，疏衰，菲，杖。入自闕，升自西階。如小斂，則子免而從柩，入自門，升自阼階。君大夫士一節也。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「共殯服，則子麻，弁絰，疏衰，菲，杖。入自闕，升自西階。如小斂，則子免而從柩，入自門，升自阼階。君大夫士一節也。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0075", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 75, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [75]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「君之喪既引，聞父母之喪，如之何？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「君之喪既引，聞父母之喪，如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0076", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 76, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [76]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「遂。既封而歸，不俟子。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「遂。既封而歸，不俟子。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0077", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 77, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [77]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「父母之喪既引，及涂，聞君薨，如之何？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「父母之喪既引，及涂，聞君薨，如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0078", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 78, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [78]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「遂。既封，改服而往。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「遂。既封，改服而往。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0079", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 79, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [79]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「宗子為士，庶子為大夫，其祭也如之何？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「宗子為士，庶子為大夫，其祭也如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0080", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 80, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [80]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「以上牲祭於宗子之家。祝曰：『孝子某為介子某薦其常事。』若宗子有罪，居于他國，庶子為大夫，其祭也，祝曰：『孝子某使介子某執其常事。』攝主不厭祭，不旅，不假，不綏祭，不配。布奠於賓，賓奠而不舉，不歸肉。其辭於賓曰：『宗兄、宗弟、宗子在他國，使某辭。』」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「以上牲祭於宗子之家。祝曰：『孝子某為介子某薦其常事。』若宗子有罪，居于他國，庶子為大夫，其祭也，祝曰：『孝子某使介子某執其常事。』攝主不厭祭，不旅，不假，不綏祭，不配。布奠於賓，賓奠而不舉，不歸肉。其辭於賓曰：『宗兄、宗弟、宗子在他國，使某辭。』」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0081", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 81, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [81]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「宗子去在他國，庶子無爵而居者，可以祭乎？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「宗子去在他國，庶子無爵而居者，可以祭乎？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0082", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 82, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [82]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「祭哉！」請問：「其祭如之何？」孔子曰：「望墓而為壇，以時祭。若宗子死，告於墓而後祭於家。宗子死，稱名不言孝，身沒而已。子游之徒，有庶子祭者以此，若義也。今之祭者，不首其義，故誣於祭也。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「祭哉！」請問：「其祭如之何？」孔子曰：「望墓而為壇，以時祭。若宗子死，告於墓而後祭於家。宗子死，稱名不言孝，身沒而已。子游之徒，有庶子祭者以此，若義也。今之祭者，不首其義，故誣於祭也。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0083", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 83, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [83]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「祭必有尸乎？若厭祭亦可乎？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「祭必有尸乎？若厭祭亦可乎？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0084", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 84, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [84]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「祭成喪者必有尸，尸必以孫。孫幼，則使人抱之。無孫，則取於同姓可也。祭殤必厭，蓋弗成也。祭成喪而無尸，是殤之也。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「祭成喪者必有尸，尸必以孫。孫幼，則使人抱之。無孫，則取於同姓可也。祭殤必厭，蓋弗成也。祭成喪而無尸，是殤之也。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0085", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 85, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [85]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「有陰厭，有陽厭。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「有陰厭，有陽厭。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0086", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 86, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [86]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「殤不祔祭，何謂陰厭、陽厭？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「殤不祔祭，何謂陰厭、陽厭？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0087", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 87, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [87]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「宗子為殤而死，庶子弗為後也。其吉祭，特牲。祭殤不舉，無肵俎，無玄酒，不告利成，是謂陰厭。凡殤，與無後者，祭於宗子之家，當室之白，尊于東房，是謂陽厭。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「宗子為殤而死，庶子弗為後也。其吉祭，特牲。祭殤不舉，無肵俎，無玄酒，不告利成，是謂陰厭。凡殤，與無後者，祭於宗子之家，當室之白，尊于東房，是謂陽厭。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0088", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 88, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [88]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「葬引至於堩，日有食之，則有變乎？且不乎？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「葬引至於堩，日有食之，則有變乎？且不乎？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0089", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 89, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [89]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「昔者吾從老聃助葬於巷黨，及堩，日有食之，老聃曰：『丘！止柩，就道右，止哭以聽變。』既明反而後行。曰：『禮也。』反葬，而丘問之曰：『夫柩不可以反者也，日有食之，不知其已之遲數，則豈如行哉？』老聃曰：『諸侯朝天子，見日而行，逮日而舍奠；大夫使，見日而行，逮日而舍。夫柩不早出，不暮宿。見星而行者，唯罪人與奔父母之喪者乎！日有食之，安知其不見星也？且君子行禮，不以人之親痁患。』吾聞諸老聃云。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「昔者吾從老聃助葬於巷黨，及堩，日有食之，老聃曰：『丘！止柩，就道右，止哭以聽變。』既明反而後行。曰：『禮也。』反葬，而丘問之曰：『夫柩不可以反者也，日有食之，不知其已之遲數，則豈如行哉？』老聃曰：『諸侯朝天子，見日而行，逮日而舍奠；大夫使，見日而行，逮日而舍。夫柩不早出，不暮宿。見星而行者，唯罪人與奔父母之喪者乎！日有食之，安知其不見星也？且君子行禮，不以人之親痁患。』吾聞諸老聃云。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0090", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 90, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [90]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「為君使而卒於舍，禮曰：公館復，私館不復。凡所使之國，有司所授舍，則公館已，何謂私館不復也？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「為君使而卒於舍，禮曰：公館復，私館不復。凡所使之國，有司所授舍，則公館已，何謂私館不復也？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0091", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 91, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [91]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「善乎問之也！自卿、大夫、士之家，曰私館；公館與公所為，曰公館。公館復，此之謂也。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「善乎問之也！自卿、大夫、士之家，曰私館；公館與公所為，曰公館。公館復，此之謂也。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0092", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 92, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [92]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「下殤：土周葬于園，遂輿機而往，途邇故也。今墓遠，則其葬也如之何？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「下殤：土周葬于園，遂輿機而往，途邇故也。今墓遠，則其葬也如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0093", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 93, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [93]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「吾聞諸老聃曰：昔者史佚有子而死，下殤也。墓遠，召公謂之曰：『何以不棺斂於宮中？』史佚曰：『吾敢乎哉？』召公言於周公，周公曰：『豈不可？』史佚行之。下殤用棺衣棺，自史佚始也。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「吾聞諸老聃曰：昔者史佚有子而死，下殤也。墓遠，召公謂之曰：『何以不棺斂於宮中？』史佚曰：『吾敢乎哉？』召公言於周公，周公曰：『豈不可？』史佚行之。下殤用棺衣棺，自史佚始也。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0094", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 94, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [94]", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「卿、大夫將為尸於公，受宿矣，而有齊衰內喪，則如之何？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「卿、大夫將為尸於公，受宿矣，而有齊衰內喪，則如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0095", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 95, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [95]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「出，舍於公館以待事，禮也。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「出，舍於公館以待事，禮也。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0096", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 96, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [96]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「尸弁冕而出，卿、大夫、士皆下之，尸必式，必有前驅。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「尸弁冕而出，卿、大夫、士皆下之，尸必式，必有前驅。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0097", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 97, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [97]", "text_original": "子夏問曰：「三年之喪卒哭，金革之事無辟也者，禮與？初有司與？」", "text_normalized": "子夏問曰：「三年之喪卒哭，金革之事無辟也者，禮與？初有司與？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0098", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 98, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [98]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「夏后氏三年之喪，既殯而致事，殷人既葬而致事。《記》曰：『君子不奪人之親，亦不可奪親也。』此之謂乎？」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「夏后氏三年之喪，既殯而致事，殷人既葬而致事。《記》曰：『君子不奪人之親，亦不可奪親也。』此之謂乎？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0099", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 99, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [99]", "text_original": "子夏曰：「金革之事無辟也者，非與？」", "text_normalized": "子夏曰：「金革之事無辟也者，非與？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__zh-0100", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__chinesenotes-liji-zh-1f6b1d3", "text_language": "zh", "segment_type": "block", "segment_position": 100, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 [100]", "text_original": "孔子曰：「吾聞諸老聃曰：昔者魯公伯禽有為為之也。今以三年之喪，從其利者，吾弗知也！」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「吾聞諸老聃曰：昔者魯公伯禽有為為之也。今以三年之喪，從其利者，吾弗知也！」", "notes": ""}
